    %% --- RELACIONES Y FLUJOS ---
    
    Views -->|data-i18n, fetch| JS
    Views -->|HTTP GET/POST| App
    App -->|enrutamiento| Routes
    Routes -->|auth, locals| Middleware
    Routes -->|lógica| Controllers
    Controllers -->|Mongoose CRUD| Models
    Controllers -->|audit, pdf, csv| Utils
    Models -->|ODM| Mongo
    Utils -->|generar PDF| PDF
    Utils -->|generar CSV| CSV
    Controllers -->|avatar| Upload
    Middleware -->|verificar token| JWT

    %% --- RELACIONES ESTRUCTURALES IMPLÍCITAS ---
    Views -.->|estilos| CSS
    Views -.->|render| Ejs
    JS -.->|UI Alerts| Swal
    JS -.->|tablas dinámicas| DT
    App -.->|framework| Express
    Models -.->|driver| Mongoose
    Middleware -.->|encriptación| Bcrypt